claim.claim-text:
1. A toy comprising: 
a) a base; 
b) a rotating element on the base, wherein the rotating element is adapted to rotate about an axis; 
c) a first set of image elements on the rotating element, wherein each image element in the first set is positioned at a first radial distance from the axis; and 
d) a second set of image elements on the rotating element, wherein each image element in the second set is positioned at a second radial distance from the axis, 
wherein the first distance is different than the second distance.

17. A toy comprising: 
a) a base; 
b) a rotating element on the base, wherein the rotating element rotates about an axis; 
c) a set of image elements on the rotating element, wherein each image element in the set is positioned at a radial distance from the axis; and 
d) an actuator coupled to the rotating element.
